1
00:00:02,002 --> 00:00:03,303
Bai Xing, are you crying?

2
00:00:04,771 --> 00:00:06,306
Did Hei Yan do something to you?

3
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:08,240
No, not at all.

4
00:00:09,376 --> 00:00:10,936
Thank you all for coming to support me.

5
00:00:10,977 --> 00:00:12,145
This is my first time acting,

6
00:00:12,979 --> 00:00:14,513
and I'm sure you're all
just as excited as I am.

7
00:00:14,514 --> 00:00:15,181
Right?

8
00:00:15,415 --> 00:00:16,415
But...

9
00:00:16,783 --> 00:00:18,051
without the idol filter,

10
00:00:18,284 --> 00:00:20,012
I wasn't sure if I could
actually do a good job.

11
00:00:21,521 --> 00:00:24,324
Luckily, I had Hei Yan by my side.

12
00:00:27,527 --> 00:00:29,194
I know a lot of fans

13
00:00:29,195 --> 00:00:30,462
were really against me and Hei Yan

14
00:00:30,463 --> 00:00:31,598
working together at first.

15
00:00:31,998 --> 00:00:34,033
Some of you didn't even like him.

16
00:00:34,601 --> 00:00:36,636
But you can't judge a book by its cover.

17
00:00:37,036 --> 00:00:38,036
See?

18
00:00:39,672 --> 00:00:40,706
He's actually really
easy to get along with.

19
00:00:40,707 --> 00:00:42,067
Don't let his size intimidate you.

20
00:00:43,843 --> 00:00:44,744
That's not it!

21
00:00:44,745 --> 00:00:46,278
I love you so much,

22
00:00:46,279 --> 00:00:48,079
but now you're just
throwing yourself at him?

23
00:00:48,281 --> 00:00:49,649
Why do you have to be in a "ship"?

24
00:00:54,387 --> 00:00:55,487
I just want to support you alone.

25
00:00:55,488 --> 00:00:56,856
Is that too much to ask?

26
00:01:05,365 --> 00:01:07,667
On stage, I'm a singer and a dancer.

27
00:01:08,001 --> 00:01:10,370
In front of the camera, I'm an actor.

28
00:01:10,637 --> 00:01:11,804
But in private,

29
00:01:11,805 --> 00:01:13,372
I'm just a human being with feelings,

30
00:01:13,373 --> 00:01:15,075
flaws, and emotions.

31
00:01:15,975 --> 00:01:17,544
I think from now on,

32
00:01:18,178 --> 00:01:19,412
you could try to love

33
00:01:19,746 --> 00:01:21,266
the version of me that's with Hei Yan.

34
00:01:40,533 --> 00:01:41,533
I need you to be okay,

35
00:01:42,202 --> 00:01:43,202
because only then

36
00:01:43,603 --> 00:01:45,004
can I be okay too.

37
00:01:47,807 --> 00:01:48,807
Alright, enough.

38
00:01:52,979 --> 00:01:54,814
You and the director are so annoying.

39
00:01:55,381 --> 00:01:57,317
What kind of script was that?

40
00:01:58,518 --> 00:02:00,854
You made Youzhi look like some heartbreaker

41
00:02:01,414 --> 00:02:03,182
who's just playing dumb.

42
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:06,025
You did a great job.

43
00:02:06,526 --> 00:02:07,694
It felt so real.

44
00:02:08,061 --> 00:02:09,061
Honestly,

45
00:02:09,162 --> 00:02:10,842
I think you actually have feelings for me.

46
00:02:37,824 --> 00:02:40,659
Watch the wardrobe! We have continuity.
You're getting snot all over my clothes.

47
00:02:40,660 --> 00:02:42,060
Well, you're the one who hugged me.

48
00:02:46,299 --> 00:02:47,800
You're so heartless.

49
00:02:48,668 --> 00:02:50,035
Just like A-You.

50
00:02:50,036 --> 00:02:52,104
Heartless... irresponsible...

51
00:02:52,105 --> 00:02:53,373
You're all the same.

52
00:02:55,475 --> 00:02:56,475
Fine, fine.

53
00:02:56,576 --> 00:02:57,576
Tell you what,

54
00:02:57,810 --> 00:02:59,279
I'll make you something good to eat.

55
00:03:03,049 --> 00:03:04,150
What are you making?

56
00:03:05,151 --> 00:03:07,420
Whatever you're in the mood for.

57
00:03:08,321 --> 00:03:09,321
Let's go.

58
00:03:15,962 --> 00:03:16,962
Let's go.

59
00:03:18,431 --> 00:03:20,098
I want pasta.

60
00:03:20,099 --> 00:03:21,099
And?

61
00:03:21,267 --> 00:03:22,334
And hot pot.

62
00:03:22,335 --> 00:03:23,335
And?

63
00:03:23,403 --> 00:03:24,403
And...

64
00:03:25,738 --> 00:03:26,738
You're such a pig.
